8)how to swap two bits
10110,1,3
op- 11100

bit1=n>>1 & 1 =00001
bit2= n>>3 &1 =00000
mask1=1<<1 =00010
n=n^mask1= 10110^00010=10100

mask2=1<<3 = 01000
n^mask2= 10100^01000 =11100

